name: Deathstalker and the Warriors from Hell
Revenge of the Creature
summary: Mike Nelson, Crow, Tom Servo and Cambot Riff the classic horror movie 'Revenge of the Creature'. in their hilarious style. They Meet Dr. Foresters relative who has become the Lawgiver of Professor Bobo and are forced to keep watching movies just as they thought they had escaped from their fate.

name: The Leech Woman
summary: Deep in the heart of the jungle lives a tribe that holds the secret to youth, a doctor, his wife and her lawyer set out on a expedition to discover this incredible secret after a old tribal woman visits his office. This is the movie that Mike Nelson and his robot cronies are forced to watch this time up in space on their strange space station. Meanwhile Crow sets his nanobots to work repairing the satellite and Professor Bobo and his friends start to question if Pearl is really the Lawgiver.

name: The Mole People
summary: Mike Nelson and his robot buddies on the Satellite of Love are forced to watch a 1950's movie 'The Mole People'. The Mole People are discovered to live deep underground in a mountainous region of Asia when a professor leads a expedition in an attempt to discover a ancient civilization high on a mountain top. Professor Bobo and his fellow apes celebrate Lawgiver day.

name: The Deadly Mantis
summary: Deep in the bowels of the Satellite of Love, Mike, Crow and Tom Servo sit in the theater forced to watch 'The Deadly Mantis'. The Deadly giant Mantis first appears in the cold wastes of the Arctic where a observation station is destroyed. The crew tries to hold their sanity together with their usual off the wall quips during the movie. Meanwhile on the Satellite of Love, Crow decides that it is casual business day and down on Earth professor Bobo and his buddies help some strange people fix their Holy Bomb.

name: The Thing That Couldn't Die
summary: In the bowels of the Satellite a movie is playing, possible buried treasure leads to entrapment when a young lady with dousing skills makes a gruesome discovery on a farm. Meanwhile Mike Nelson, Crow, Tom Servo and the others meet the Observers for the first time.Crow decides to hold a art show.

name: The Undead
summary: The bad movie the crew is forced to watch this time involves a woman who volunteers to be hypnotized. She then experiences a past life that involves being accused of witchcraft. Tom Servo is chosen by the Observers to join them.

name: Terror from the Year 5000
summary: This week Mike Nelson, Crow and Tom Servo are forced to watch a movie where a professor has built a machine that is able to bring objects back from a future time. Tom servo decides that is is very important to comfort rate everything on the Satellite. The Observers decide they have had enough of the Lawgiver and they force Pearl to fight professor Bobo to the death.

name: The Incredibly Strange Creatures Who Stopped Living and Became Mixed-Up Zombies!!?
